==English==

===Noun===

# A [[blanket]] that one uses to have a secure [[feeling]] or reduced [[anxiety]], usually in the early years of life: ''Linus van Pelt had a famous '''security blanket'''.''
# Any [[object]] one uses to have a sense of security or reduced anxiety: ''That rabbit's foot is his '''security blanket'''.''

==Etymology==

From Linus van Pelt's [[security]] blanket in Charles Schulz's [[comic strip]] ''Peanuts''